snippet.title: Nutz Revenge IndieMania Presentation - Developer Insight
snippet.description:
Take a look at our presentation during IndieMania! We talk a bit about our goals and inspirations for Nutz Revenge, the follow that up with the trailer!

Follow for Nintendo Switch updates! 

Wishlist on Steam!
